divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting in my mom's car when i noticed a small circle about 1 centimeter in diameter on the moon on the way home i kept an eye on it. it just sat there and did not move.once i got home i sat on the roof of my house and stared at it confused i went in side after that day i never saw it again.
Summary: I looked as if some one had placed a small metal plate on the moon.
